# Locked stack

**Use:** Claude (stateless) by default, Prisma, Supabase Postgres, Supabase Storage (via `StorageProvider` only), Stripe Connect, custom auth, Fastify API, Next.js web.

**Forbidden:** LangGraph, agent frameworks, Supabase Auth, Outlook calendar. OpenAI product APIs remain out of MVP scope.

**AI:** Structured JSON output; app executes actions; confidence threshold 0.8; escalate below.

**Founder staging override:** When Anthropic has no credits, staging may use `AI_PROVIDER=openai_compatible` with Groq (`OPENAI_COMPAT_*`). Production target remains Anthropic Claude.

**API-first:** Business logic in `apps/api` only. Web uses typed API client + TanStack Query. No Prisma in web. No Server Actions as canonical writes.

**MVP channel:** Authenticated in-app web chat (primary; founder override). Twilio SMS ingress still supported. WhatsApp and anonymous web widget are V2.
